<subSubSection id="403714E33EC9D8B8BE9446FF75FFE148" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" type="notes">
<paragraph id="B143978C23E1AA5CB270BA3D39516033" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997">Notes</paragraph>
<paragraph id="ABFB5B00F9878C7837663CEF47606041" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997">
The species resembles 
<taxonomicName id="B4369AE6DCE72D6FD39F9517FF8AE782" class="Polychaeta" family="Eunicidae" genus="Leodice" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Leodice laurillardi" order="Eunicida" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" phylum="Annelida" rank="species" species="laurillardi">Leodice laurillardi</taxonomicName>
(Quatrefages, 1866) in a number of diagnostic characters. The latter was synonymised with 
<taxonomicName id="0D2BF782D0731AC57B71A840106F1903" class="Polychaeta" family="Eunicidae" genus="Leodice" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Leodice torquat" order="Eunicida" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" phylum="Annelida" rank="species" species="torquat">Leodice torquat</taxonomicName>
a by 
<bibRefCitation id="BDDEE3B4AAA3D20A3B917273BBC41406" author="Pruvot, G." journalOrPublisher="Archives de Zoologie Experimentale et Generale" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" pagination="378 - 385" title="Materiaux pour la faune des annelides de Banyuls" volume="3" year="1895">Pruvot and Racovitza (1895)</bibRefCitation>
; this was accepted by 
<bibRefCitation id="E84323864254FEBF938A8FBD6BADBC82" author="Fauvel, P." journalOrPublisher="Paul Lechevalier, Paris" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" title="Faune de France: Polychetes errantes" year="1923">Fauvel (1923)</bibRefCitation>
and later authors. However, 
<bibRefCitation id="2D13A54CC77F260124D671F873D9BB89" author="Fauchald, Kristian" journalOrPublisher="Smithsonian Contributions to Zoology" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" pagination="1 - 422" title="A Review of the Genus Eunice (Polychaeta: Eunicidae) Based upon Type Material" volume="523" year="1992">Fauchald (1992)</bibRefCitation>
resurrected 
<taxonomicName id="6C4D2D80B33C83851606F24725BCF0F4" class="Polychaeta" family="Eunicidae" genus="Leodice" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Leodice laurillardi" order="Eunicida" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" phylum="Annelida" rank="species" species="laurillardi">Leodice laurillardi</taxonomicName>
as a valid species and 
<bibRefCitation id="0455FDD44664FD565DBF5BC1410D4514" author="Arias, A." journalOrPublisher="Zootaxa" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" pagination=": 475" title="Rediscovery and redescription of Leodicelaurillardi (Quatrefages, 1866) comb. nov. (Annelida: Eunicidae) - a rare European polychaete or just an overlooked species?" volume="3964" year="2015">Arias et al. (2015)</bibRefCitation>
re-described the species based on type material and new specimens from the Mediterranean. They suggest that 
<taxonomicName id="BC465D9F877F8D563CD4724F28551C70" class="Polychaeta" family="Eunicidae" genus="Leodice" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Leodice laurillardi" order="Eunicida" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" phylum="Annelida" rank="species" species="laurillardi">Leodice laurillardi</taxonomicName>
could be much more widespread than previously thought but was possibly being overlooked in the Mediterranean due to the confusion with 
<taxonomicName id="63DEA70FD66D834DB14838C1F6A7F70A" class="Polychaeta" family="Eunicidae" genus="Leodice" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Leodice torquata" order="Eunicida" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" phylum="Annelida" rank="species" species="torquata">Leodice torquata</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
